    public class EquinoxDriverImpl
extends AbstractFactoryDriverImpl
implements EquinoxDriver
    An implementation of the model object 'Equinox Driver'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • User Service
    • Instance Number
    • Access Credentials
    • Security Configuration
